Take & Bake ‚Äî 13 pre-made, frozen mini churros ready to reheat, fill and devour  Each kit includes:  One devil's dozen [13] pre-made, frozen mini churros coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon One reusable filling bottle of your choice of either dulce de leche, nutella or sweet cream One free churro coupon for curbside order  Reheat at 350 degrees for about 6 minutes or until they are your desired temperature. Fill to your hearts' content! For added flavor pop, we humbly suggest sprinkling some pink Himalayan salt on top!

column4: Take & Bake Anytime-at-home Churros ‚ Refill of Devil's Dozen (13) Churros
column6: One devil's dozen [13] pre-made, frozen mini churros coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon ready to reheat and fill.  Reheat at 350 degrees for about 6 minutes or until they are your desired temperature. Get creative with your filling choices! We humbly suggest honey, jam, dulce de leche, nutella, peanut or almond butter, whipped cream, custard, chocolate and fresh fruit!

Give yourself some filling flavor options with an extra reusable bottle of your choice of dulce de leche, nutella or sweet cream!  * Note: Churros in photo are just to get you salivating but aren't included with the extra filling bottle.
